{"tid":1684691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓軍：朝鮮向東海發射兩枚不明飛行物","createTime":"2019-10-31T08:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T08:37:02.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f222f07393458fd8a629545ecae9db298c759f6","tid":1684691,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"韓國聯合參謀本部表示，朝鮮今午（31日）由平安南道向東海發射兩枚不明飛行物，韓軍正監察朝解會否再有進一步試射等情況。<br />\n<br />\n這是朝鮮今年第12次試射飛行物，對上一次是本月2日試射可搭載核彈頭的「北極星-3」型潛射彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20191031/s00005/1572509659651/%e3%80%90%e6%9c%9d%e9%ae%ae%e9%a2%a8%e9%9b%b2%e3%80%91%e9%9f%93%e8%bb%8d-%e6%9c%9d%e9%ae%ae%e5%90%91%e6%9d%b1%e6%b5%b7%e7%99%bc%e5%b0%84%e5%85%a9%e6%9e%9a%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%8e%e9%a3%9b%e8%a1%8c%e7%89%a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00005%2F1572509659651%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%259c%259d%25e9%25ae%25ae%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e9%259b%25b2%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%259f%2593%25e8%25bb%258d-%25e6%259c%259d%25e9%25ae%25ae%25e5%2590%2591%25e6%259d%25b1%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%259e%259a%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%25a3%259b%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2589%25a9&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=739ba5a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00005%2F1572509659651%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%259c%259d%25e9%25ae%25ae%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e9%259b%25b2%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%259f%2593%25e8%25bb%258d-%25e6%259c%259d%25e9%25ae%25ae%25e5%2590%2591%25e6%259d%25b1%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%259e%259a%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%25a3%259b%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2589%25a9&h=f74bbd58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20191031/s00005/1572509659651/%e3%80%90%e6%9c%9d%e9%ae%ae